Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P2711 Newspapers.
    P3269 Pottery Products, NEC.
    P1382 Oil and Gas Exploration Services.
    P1389 Oil and Gas Field Services, NEC.
    P3262 Vitreous China Table and Kitchenware.
